Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}君を理解し続けたい
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}I’m on your side　護ってあげる
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}黑白难辨
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.87,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}暧昧不明
